<p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; text-combine: letters"></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; text-combine: letters">서비스 해지 메뉴를 통해 발송된 문자메시지</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; text-combine: letters">(SMS) </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; text-combine: letters">또는 이메일</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; text-combine: letters">(E-mail)</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; text-combine: letters">을 통해 본인확인 후 서비스 해지를 할 수 있습니다</span></p></div></div><!----><!----></div></div></div><div class="c-accordion-group"><div variant="primary" class="c-accordion-header collapsed" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="_uid_472_9" style="overflow-anchor: none;"><strong class="w-auto">[로그인플러스] 서비스 사용 요금은 얼마인가요?</strong> <div class="acc-toggle"><i class="when-open"></i> <i class="when-closed"></i></div></div> <div id="_uid_472_9" class="collapse" style="display: none;"><div class="card"><!----><!----><div class="card-body"><!----><!----><div class="contentsWrap"><p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; language: ko; text-combine: letters">서비스 사용 요금은 월정액</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; language: en-US; text-combine: letters"> </span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; language: ko; text-combine: letters">1,100원(부가세 포함</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; language: en-US; text-combine: letters">)입니다.</span></p>
<p><span style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 맑은 고딕; COLOR: black; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; language: ko; text-combine: letters"></span>&nbsp;</p>
